0:

”Alexa, start Tahitian Waterfalls”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: tahitian waterfalls
des:
NEW - Just Released! No Ads. No Talking. Just soothing, gentle waterfalls.

Only in Tahiti, the soothing sounds of water flowing down from above ... There's nothing like it to put you into a gentle slumber. 

Easy to use. Enable Tahitian Waterfalls for your Alexa. Then just say: "Alexa, open Tahitian Waterfalls."

If you like, set a sleep timer by saying "Alexa, set sleep timer for x minutes."

Meditate, relax, sleep, concentrate, study with the soothing sound of Tahitian Waterfalls.

Any questions or suggestions?
Emails welcome at Support@SayGoodMorning.org.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
